<section class="section bg-gray-50" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-section bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-6 md:p-8">
        {% faqItem "When did Universal Epic Universe open?" %}
          <p>Universal Epic Universe opened on <strong>May 22, 2025</strong>. It's Universal Orlando's third theme park and the largest Universal park ever built, spanning 110 acres of themed area. The park features five immersive worlds including Super Nintendo World, the Wizarding World's Ministry of Magic, and Dark Universe featuring classic monsters.</p>
        {% endfaqItem %}

        {% faqItem "What is the world's tallest roller coaster?" %}
          <p><strong>Falcon's Flight at Six Flags Qiddiya City</strong> in Saudi Arabia holds the world record as the tallest roller coaster at 640 feet (195 meters). It's also the world's fastest at 155 mph and longest at 2.6 miles. The coaster opened December 31, 2025.</p>
        {% endfaqItem %}

        {% faqItem "What theme parks offer rain check policies?" %}
          <p>Major parks with rain check policies include: <strong>SeaWorld/Busch Gardens</strong> (Weather-or-Not Assurance - 12 month return), <strong>Holiday World</strong> (Worry-Free Weather Guarantee), <strong>Silver Dollar City</strong> (Sunny Day Guarantee), <strong>Dollywood</strong> (Rain Check), and <strong>Hersheypark</strong> (Return Visit Voucher). Note: Disney, Universal, Cedar Point, and most Six Flags parks do NOT offer rain checks.</p>
        {% endfaqItem %}

        {% faqItem "Is Express Pass worth it at Universal?" %}
          <p>Express Pass is worth it during <strong>peak seasons</strong> (spring break, summer, holidays) when standby waits exceed 60+ minutes. At Epic Universe, Express Pass costs $140-$360+ per person. For off-peak visits with early arrival, you can often experience all major attractions without it. Use our <a href="/tools/express-pass-calculator/">Express Pass ROI Calculator</a> to determine value for your specific trip.</p>
        {% endfaqItem %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

